author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 
 
Check out the full three-song session of Big Thief from 2017 on our channel. #VaultSessions #TheCurrent #BigThief
title: Big Thief performs "Mythological Beauty" in 2017 #BigThief
